snippet.title: Defending Johnny Depp. WTF, WB?!? #AmberTurd #BringBackJohnny #boondockstallyns #FantasticBeasts
snippet.description:
Howdy Neighbor!!
First off, please forgive me for seeming a little short in my video. I'm not happy about this.

Today I'm Talking about Johnny Depp Being fired from his role as Gellert Grindelwald in the Fantastic Beasts and where to find them series.

Please don't forget to leave a #AmberTurd in the comments an when sharing this video.
